Hey Streamlitters! 
 
October is upon us, and you’re in for a treat—release 1.39 brings new functionalities that let you do even more with your apps. Keep reading to see highlights from the release, how to dive deeper into these features at the Quarterly Showcase, and where to find your next project idea.
&#128680;  Release 1.39
Highlights 



	- &#127908; Introducing st.experimental_audio_input <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGWY2mPXMBOAxQQfXLxGGzQ1HZA9o6Ilnxx_DDilcU4r1yE0_7jKDON7xINAXj8Iwwwvk_jP78=> to record with microphones.
	- &#128205; st.pydeck_chart can return selection events.
	- &#128512;	st.button, st.download_button, st.form_submit_button, st.link_button, and st.popover can include an icon.
	- &#127970; st.logo now has adjustable size.
	- &#129517; st.navigation lets you display an always-expanded or collapsible menu.


See the full changelog <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGWY2mPXKj1R-iU8p-H_JAJG0UwqJdfGuu--9A8iPQrBLGfg9sGJk42cJuvwdBOv06mqZQGBzs=> and download the latest version of Streamlit.
&#128161; Join the Quarterly Showcase
The Quarterly Showcase is back! Don’t miss your once-in-a-quarter chance to hang with the team and fellow community members as we dive into everything new in Streamlit. You’ll hear from one of the Streamlit co-founders, chat with the product engineers, and see cool, real-world demos. This virtual event will take place on October 30, at 10 a.m. PT. 
 
See the full agenda and RSVP here! <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGWY2mPXOF4j_XlMBkxvA6t3dNC41aOYHLtjqJze59fYet_lNUX8SiwT5865tqHJ-zqp8QBnoM=> &#127880;
